Rudy Squeeze Detect v2 — Volatility Breakout Detector for high-beta equities. Identifies squeeze setups using volume
surge, price gaps, Bollinger Band compression, and 5-day momentum. Scores each signal (minimum 3) with weighted
factors: volume ratio, gap percentage, EMA alignment, and momentum. Exits via trailing stop or momentum fade (price
below short MA with negative 5-day momentum). Designed for: GME, AMC, SOFI, RIVN, LCID, COIN, MARA, RIOT, PLTR.


